                            <p>Floors are equally important as any other part of the house. Flooring is one of the most important aspects of the house or business. It adds to the charm and beauty of your living or office space The floor is that part of the building on which the and occupants move and materials are stored. It is a horizontal component of a building structure, which divides the building into the different level for the purpose of creating more accommodation within a restricted space one above the other and provide support for a building. The floor covering or flooring provides a smooth, clean, impervious, durable, colourful, hard and attractive surface. It is the cover which has to offer resistance to wear and tear due to human movement.</p>

                                </div>
